  "remarks": "National identification no: China 653225197110100533 (Chinese national identity card number). Overall leader and commander of the Eastern Turkistan Islamic Movement (QDe.088). Involved in fundraising and recruitment for this organization. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. Photo available for inclusion in the INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link: https://www.interpol.int/en/notice/search/un/1558612.; Listing: Listed on: 15 April 2009 (amended on 13 Dec. 2011, 20 Jun. 2017, 24 Nov. 2020, 11 Mar. 2025)",
